high_descs: Move to the plant in the corner.
Pick up the watering can from the floor.
Bring the watering can to the black desk.
Put the watering can on the black desk.

Continue around the table, turning right to go between the table and two red chairs, then forward to the black desk.
Put the watering can spout side down on the desk in front of the box.
anns.task_desc: Place a white watering can on a black desk.

Turn around, walk to the black table
Put the pot on the table
